Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Welcome to The Offices at Grandin Parc Village. This six story office building is undergoing a full exterior & interior renovation with high quality flexible space ready for occupancy in early 2019. The extensive renovation includes the creation of new modern building amenities such as a new expanded lobby, a fitness centre, a business centre with boardroom, and a large outdoor plaza with 1,800 square feet of new ground floor retail space including space for a proposed coffee shop. The hallways, washrooms, mechanical and elevator systems are being completely renovated and retrofitted. The exterior of the building will also be given a new modern look with new windows throughout.
